summary: Between 2004 and 2012, patients with pT1-3, pN0-3, M0 breast tumors were randomised between adjuvant dose-dense doxorubicin-cyclophosphamide (ddAC) versus docetaxel-doxorubicin-cyclophosphamide (TAC). Trial registration numbers: ISRCTN61893718 and BOOG 2004-04.
title: Matador,a multicenter clinical trial. Non-metastatic breast cancer patients were randomized between TAC or ddAC
